response.original_title: Rodrigo y Gabriela: Live at Red Rocks 2013
response.overview: Recorded live on 28 July 2013 at Red Rocks Amphitheatre, Morrison, Colorado with special guests the Colorado Symphony.  Set list:  Savitri  The Russian Messenger  Somnium  Torito  Hanuman  11:11  Logos  Hora Zero  Diablo Rojo  The Soundmaker  Fram  Tamacun
